{"tid":294972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7菲律賓男子 男扮女裝賣淫被捕","createTime":"2017-06-23T11:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T13:23:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8de201e5824b9681ae0e9bd11756f8154544df19","tid":294972,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/194716_5acbff93797288a7e5f658570ae347d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F194716_5acbff93797288a7e5f658570ae347d3.jpg&h=ba482a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/194717_a64d0a50ba57e7aceb2c5eebfd89ee82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F194717_a64d0a50ba57e7aceb2c5eebfd89ee82.jpg&h=af8d0ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n治安警反賣淫行動帶走17男女，當中包括七名作性感女性打扮的菲律賓男子，現時已交由情報廳和出入境事務廳作進一步處理。<br />\n治安警今日凌晨在新口岸和城市日大馬路一帶採取行動，截查到合共17名年齡介乎20至40歲的男女懷疑從事賣淫活動，其中除<span style=\"color: red;\">七名作性感女性打扮的菲律賓男子外</span>，其餘十名均是中國護照的內地女子。她/他們全部報稱無業，經查問後承認以新口岸區一帶夜場人士為賣淫目標。至於有否受人操控及每次肉金多少則需待治安警進一步調查。"},{"pid":"cc1f08c2ac07554fecd0b79ef4824e2a4f06da1b","tid":294972,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"You竟然是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c569dd7ee51cdf6d6df1edc6082ad7901264a265","tid":294972,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"想挑戰秦國偽娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3739b8bf678a117affc3a6f87db046fc097382","tid":294972,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a51409dffe79c9f11cd2ceb4dc381f84a1c4203","tid":294972,"uid":54373,"like":